    "The mission of the Law Department is to provide a high level of professional legal services to its clients, the Mayor, City Council and City departments, supporting all official capacities within City government, in a timely and cost effective manner. Law Department personnel are committed to upholding the highest ethical standards and to assuming a professional and caring attitude toward their clients, and among themselves."
